{
  "texts": [
    "Typically, the self-supervised training objective is same with that for pre-training, and the learning rate is much smaller than than for pre-training.",
    "Continued pre-training is a important stage for constructing vertical domain LLMs.",
    "However, it is highly computational expensive, which impedes the development of vertical domain LLMs, especailly for the organizations with limited computational resources.",
    "Enhancing LoRA for continued pre-training and reducing its computational cost is worth to explored.",
    "LoRA for autonomous agentsIn LLM-based autonomous agents, the agents are assigned with specific roles."
  ]
}